OL,3,C'It's a war crime': ITV News' Gaza
OL,4,Cclip sparks outrage
OL,6,FRishi Sunak and the US were quizzed
OL,7,Fover an ITV News video which shows a
OL,8,Fcivilian being shot dead while
OL,9,Fcarrying a white flag in Gaza, many
OL,10,Fsay this shows a 'war crime,' John
OL,11,FIrvine and Robert Moore reports
OL,13,FThe "shocking video" of a man waving a
OL,14,Fwhite flag being shot dead in ,
OL,15,Freleased by ITV News, has sparked
OL,16,Faccusations of a "war crime".
