OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FIn response, Sunak said "international
OL,12,Fhumanitarian law should be respected,
OL,13,Fand civilians should be protected".
OL,15,FBut Flynn pushed further, adding: "I
OL,16,Fdon't think it's unreasonable to ask
OL,17,Fthe PM of the United Kingdom to rise
OL,18,Fto that dispatch box and tell the
OL,19,Fpeople of these isles and elsewhere,
OL,20,Fthat shooting an unarmed man walking
OL,21,Funder a white flag is a war crime.
