OL,6,F"Now in recent weeks this house has
OL,7,Facted with urgency and intent
OL,8,Ffollowing an ITV drama, the question
OL,9,Fis will this house now show the same
OL,10,Furgency and intent following this ITV
OL,11,FNews report and finally back a
OL,12,Fceasefire in Gaza."
OL,14,FSunak replied: "Mr Speaker no-one
OL,15,Fwants to see this conflict go on for a
OL,16,Fmoment longer than necessary, and we
OL,17,Fdo want to see an immediate and
OL,18,Fsustained humanitarian pause."
