OL,6,FHe added: "We have been absolutely
OL,7,Fclear throughout this that yes of
OL,8,Fcourse Israel has the right to self-
OL,9,Fdefence but it has to be in accordance
OL,10,Fto international law.
OL,12,F"It is why we have said that the
OL,13,FInternational Criminal Court should be
OL,14,Fin there with a prosecutor gathering
OL,15,Fevidence because there has to be
OL,16,Faccountability with international law."
