OL,6,F"There's no question the war between
OL,7,FIsrael and Hamas is a great tragedy.
OL,8,FAnd the death of any innocent
OL,9,Fcivilians in this conflict, whether
OL,10,Fthey be Palestinian or Israeli, is
OL,11,Ftragic.
OL,13,F"As you've heard us say, we support
OL,14,FIsrael's inherent right to defend its
OL,15,Fcitizens from terrorism.
OL,17,F"We also expect them to conduct
OL,18,Foperations in accordance with the laws
OL,19,Fof war and to help enable the flow of
OL,20,Fhumanitarian assistance to the people
OL,21,Fof Gaza."
