OL,10,Fpropaganda effort to defame the IDF
OL,11,Fand undermine our objective to
OL,12,Fdismantle Hamas and ensure the
OL,13,Fterrorist entity never again holds the
OL,14,Fpower to build a terrorist army,
OL,15,Finvade Israel, murder, burn, rape and
